- **Code Formatting / Lint:** Ruff (replaces `black`, `isort`, `flake8`)
- **Type Annotations:** Use `typing` module, all functions, methods, class members must have type annotations
- **Testing Framework:** `pytest`
- **Documentation:** Google-style docstring
- **Version Control:** `git`

